OL,3,CAfghanistan faces internet blackout
OL,4,Camid fears Taliban targeting
OL,5,C'immortality'
OL,7,FAfghanistan has entered a second day
OL,8,Fof near-total internet blackout, after
OL,9,Freports that nationwide fiber-optic
OL,10,Fservices were cut as part of a Taliban
OL,11,Fcrackdown on immorality.
OL,13,FAccording to internet-access watchdog
OL,14,FNetBlocks, online connectivity
OL,15,Fcollapsed to just 14% levels on
OL,16,FMonday, marking the first nationwide
OL,17,Fdisruption since the Taliban seized
OL,18,Fpower in August 2021.
