OL,7,FLocal media outlets and civil society
OL,8,Fsources have linked the blackout to a
OL,9,FTaliban decree earlier this month, in
OL,10,Fwhich the group's supreme leader,
OL,11,FHibatullah Akhundzada, ordered the
OL,12,Fsuspension of fiber-optic services to
OL,13,Fcurb what he described as "immoral
OL,14,Factivities."
OL,16,FThe Taliban has not clarified what
OL,17,Ffalls under this category, nor has it
OL,18,Fissued any public acknowledgment of
OL,19,Fthe blackout.
