OL,12,FBut the government relies heavily on
OL,13,Fmessaging apps and social media for
OL,14,Fits external and internal
OL,15,Fcommunications, making the Taliban's
OL,16,Fsilence all the more striking.
OL,18,FCommunication with the country appears
OL,19,Fto be impeded, with Afghans abroad
OL,20,Ftelling ITV News partner CNN they were
OL,21,Funable to reach family members inside.
