OL,7,FThe blackout has also begun to impact
OL,8,Fcritical infrastructure, with flights
OL,9,Fto Kabul airport grounded on Tuesday.
OL,11,FTracking service Flightradar24 showed
OL,12,Fseveral cancellations and dozens of
OL,13,Fflights listed as "unknown" in and out
OL,14,Fof Afghanistan's capital.
OL,16,FThe outage has raised fears of a
OL,17,Freturn to the restrictions of previous
OL,18,FTaliban rule, which banned television,
OL,19,Fsatellites and other mass
OL,20,Fcommunication devices in its war on
OL,21,Fimmorality.
