OL,7,FVulnerable communities are under
OL,8,Fparticular threat as a result of the
OL,9,Finternet suspension.
OL,11,FSince the Taliban barred girls from
OL,12,Fattending secondary school, many have
OL,13,Fturned to online classes run by
OL,14,Feducators abroad or supported by
OL,15,Fcharitable organisations.
OL,17,FWomen's rights groups warn the outage
OL,18,Fcould have devastating consequences.
